Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Ideal headquarters for a medium sized business.

Quality modern air-conditioned office and warehouse building on a good sized block of land, comprising 7 offices and a boardroom, reception area and amenities.  Downstairs to garaging/storage and a warehouse with rollerdoors - plenty of parking and room to extend.

*  Office area - 290sqm (approx)
*  Warehouse area 400sqm (approx)
*  Land 1,855sqm (approx)

207sqm* showroom/workshop/office

Separate office, lunch room, meeting room/second office

Kitchenette and bathroom

3.8m high internal clearance

Brick construction with steel frame and carpeted (carpet can be removed if needed)

Plenty of car parking immediately in front

Roller door access

Save by paying Queanbeyan prices just minutes from Fyshwick and central Canberra
